qrun v1.0
2014-05-24

OVERVIEW
--------
qrun is a lightweight qt-based application to emulate Ubuntu's alt+f2 "run" feature. This program is intentded
to be run in a similar manner, executing through an assigned hotkey.

COMPILING
---------
To install qrun, simply run these commands:
	qmake
	make
	sudo make install

COPYING
-------
The font "Droid Sans" is a humanist sans serif typeface designed by Steve Matteson, released under the
Apache License. So, it's free.

